title: 34 - Just Us (End of the Year Wrap Up)
itunes:title: 34 - Just Us (End of the Year Wrap Up)
description: Hey legends! It’s the last day of the decade, and we decided to record the final episode of 2019 with just us, your hosts, Sean Patton and Caitlin Cook, each telling a story that the other has never heard before. We’re grateful to all of you that listened in 2019, and we’re excited for 2020. Here’s five words to describe this episode: here’s to a better waffle.
